These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, jazz, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, polish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, golf, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the argentine is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the argentine is in an even position##4
5. the fan of techno is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | soul     | jazz    |
| Nationality   | polish   | argentine          | chinese   |
| Sport         | handball | weightlifting | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, garlic, cucumber
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, camping, board-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, videographer, pilot
1. the pilot is the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the pilot##3
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
4. the videographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the pilot is in an even position##4
6. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | carrot     | cucumber  | garlic  |
| Hobby   | board-games | camping | fishing    |
| Job     | paramedic      | pilot    | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cranberry, pumpkin
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, punk, jazz
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | artichoke         | pumpkin     | cranberry   |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | soul     | jazz |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, manager, chef
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, dog, hamster
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the chef##1
3. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
6. the manager is on the right of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk  | tea |
| Job        | chef | manager  | security-guard |
| Pet        | hedgehog | dog | hamster         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, fantasy
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, british, colombian
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, fish
1. the argentine is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
2. the british is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | thriller  | comedy  |
| Nationality   | british  | argentine | colombian |
| Pet           | horse  | fish    | hedgehog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, fanta
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, baking, drawing
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, ship, van
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
2. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person driving the ship is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | iced-tea  | water        |
| Hobby       | drawing | baking | writing |
| Transport   | taxi    | ship   | van   |

