.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, martial-arts
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, ferret, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, climbing
1. the person watching thriller movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | thriller        | martial-arts |
| Pet           | rabbit   | ferret      | pony     |
| Sport         | climbing | surfing | rugby    |

