.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, mango, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, coach, dancer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, baseball, parkour
1. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the dancer and the person eating raspberry##2
3. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | grapefruit   | mango | raspberry       |
| Job     | dancer  | bartender  | coach |
| Sport   | baseball | soccer  | parkour       |

