.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, singing, photography
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, british
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
3. the italian is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
4. the egyptian is on the right of the italian##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is singing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | singing | drawing | photography |
| Nationality   | british       | italian  | egyptian     |
| Pet           | frog     | turtle     | ferret          |

