.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, freelancer, lawyer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, french, turkish
1. the freelancer is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the turkish is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | lawyer | entrepreneur        | freelancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy | satire    |
| Nationality   | turkish         | brazilian      | french |

