The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, camping
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, electrician, manager
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
1. the electrician is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the nurse is in an even position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the manager is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | sudoku        | chess  | camping      |
| Job           | manager | nurse | electrician |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | animation   | superhero  |

