2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | soy-milk | iced-tea     |
| Sport       | rowing | soccer          | skateboarding |
| Transport   | train     | jet-ski          | motorbike       |

