1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person watching crime movies is the fan of country##1
5. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | western | spy |
| Music-Genre   | country        | dubstep         | folk |
| Pet           | hamster | horse         | ferret   |

