1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is in an even position##4
3. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the writer is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | writer      | nurse | fisherman |
| Pet     | pony | snake      | dog           |
| Sport   | lacrosse | tennis  | basketball    |

