.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, juice
3 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, pony
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, airplane
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | milk | juice      | 7up     |
| Pet         | rabbit  | fish | pony        |
| Transport   | skateboard | airplane    | taxi |

