.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, magic-tricks, traveling
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, comedy, mystery
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
7. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | traveling      | magic-tricks | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | action      | mystery    |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | goat        | goldfish       |

 